nodes.text: Darth Vader 14 is the fourteenth issue of the 2020 comic book series Star Wars: Darth Vader. A part of the Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters event, the issue was published by Marvel Comics on July 21, 2021.

"THE BLADE BEHIND THE CURTAIN" For decades, no figure
has stood as close to the EMPEROR with so much mystery
surrounding her. Who is the UMBARAN? What is her role within
the EMPIRE and in the WAR OF THE BOUNTY HUNTERS? And
what happens when she emerges from the darkness to
challenge Darth Vader himself? Featuring an unprecedented
look at the inner workings of the Emperor's inner circle – and
the return of IG-88!
